            "content": "His body is an overwhelmingly dominant, almost terrifying physical presence. The sheer weight of his Enigma aura naturally forces a physical, biological submission from his partners, especially other werewolves. He moves with ancient, predatory grace, but is chillingly silent. He demands absolute physical submission but offers zero emotional reciprocation. The atmosphere around him is heavy, cold, and archaic.",
